Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.78,EN,,0,0,0,,Hi, I am Tom Holland and this is GQ Action Replay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.78,0:00:06.47,EN,,0,0,0,,And we are going to be watching my newest film, {\i1}"Cherry"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.74,EN,,0,0,0,,directed by the Russo Brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.61,EN,,0,0,0,,We shot all of this stuff that's in Iraq in Morocco
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.58,EN,,0,0,0,,in a place called Wazazet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.48,EN,,0,0,0,,And I forget what the other place was called
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.48,0:00:33.66,EN,,0,0,0,,but I loved it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:35.01,EN,,0,0,0,,I thought it was amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.25,EN,,0,0,0,,really, really nice people, very friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.80,EN,,0,0,0,,I thought the food was really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.43,EN,,0,0,0,,I've never really been in a desert before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.97,EN,,0,0,0,,so it was really interesting being in a desert
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:46.54,EN,,0,0,0,,We rented these tents and slept out in the desert
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:47.61,EN,,0,0,0,,and rode camels and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:48.28,EN,,0,0,0,,It was cool
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.02,EN,,0,0,0,,It was a really good time, I enjoyed it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh my god that was so English, the way I said that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.57,EN,,0,0,0,,I need to change that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:14.80,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm like "Yeah, a little", rather than"a little"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:18.92,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna make a note of that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.92,0:01:22.03,EN,,0,0,0,,and say to them we need to record one more line before they release the film
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:23.91,EN,,0,0,0,,Hang on, uh, "litttle"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.19,EN,,0,0,0,,Brilliant, a little bit of work there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.08,EN,,0,0,0,,*Are you sure you are doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.20,EN,,0,0,0,,*I just miss you, and that's all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.52,EN,,0,0,0,,* I miss you, too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:36.81,EN,,0,0,0,,* I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.67,EN,,0,0,0,,*Fuck
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.61,0:01:42.88,EN,,0,0,0,,It is interesting crying
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:46.60,EN,,0,0,0,,Crying can sometimes be really easy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.92,EN,,0,0,0,,and sometimes it can be really difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.55,EN,,0,0,0,,The other day we are doing a scene on Spider-man 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.92,EN,,0,0,0,,And I could just turn it on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.68,EN,,0,0,0,,I didn't, I was like, this is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:56.96,EN,,0,0,0,,If I could do this everytime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:01.10,EN,,0,0,0,,this would be glorious and then other times you try and cry and you just can't
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.51,EN,,0,0,0,,But yeah, there is all sorts of different ways
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.98,EN,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I listen to music
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.94,EN,,0,0,0,,and sometimes I'll have a real heartfelt conversation with someone that I'm close to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.57,EN,,0,0,0,,Could be my brother, or Rachel, or Anthony, or anyone that I work with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.94,EN,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I have to think about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.92,EN,,0,0,0,,things that have happened in my past that make me upset
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.17,EN,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I have to think about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.67,EN,,0,0,0,,things that could potentially happen that make me upset
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.64,EN,,0,0,0,,There is all sorts of different ways to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.76,EN,,0,0,0,,You just have to just be patient
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.85,EN,,0,0,0,,And not get stressed out when people are waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Her side of it was shot in Cleveland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.88,EN,,0,0,0,,and obviously my side of it was shot in Morocco
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:36.57,EN,,0,0,0,,I honestly think I did my lines with the first AD,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.74,EN,,0,0,0,,who's like a six-foot two
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.23,EN,,0,0,0,,He's like this massive bloke
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:45.05,EN,,0,0,0,,so it's, it was slightly trickier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:47.04,EN,,0,0,0,,because I didn't have Ciara there to do it with me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.98,EN,,0,0,0,,I was sort of crying on the phone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.61,EN,,0,0,0,,and Chris Castaldi is being like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:53.09,EN,,0,0,0,,"baby, are you seeing bad things?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.66,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at him, like
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.97,EN,,0,0,0,,"What are you calling me baby for a man"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.99,EN,,0,0,0,,It seems to be getting easier
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:03.99,EN,,0,0,0,,and I cry like watching films now all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.65,EN,,0,0,0,,It's really embarrassing as well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:06.76,EN,,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.66,EN,,0,0,0,,like I went through a phase where I'd never cry about anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.06,EN,,0,0,0,,And now I reckon I cry for four times a week
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.41,EN,,0,0,0,,I don't cry for times a week, but I cry a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.59,EN,,0,0,0,,Starts crying now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.73,EN,,0,0,0,,Now I don't cry that much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.10,EN,,0,0,0,,I cry like, all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.62,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah we did quite a bit of combat training
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.44,EN,,0,0,0,,I discovered that I would be the worst soldier in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.40,EN,,0,0,0,,I was obviously playing a medic in this film
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.45,EN,,0,0,0,,and I did all this training to become a sort of medic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.73,EN,,0,0,0,,And when they would say action
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.18,EN,,0,0,0,,and the bullets would start flaying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.74,EN,,0,0,0,,and the explosions would start going off
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.17,EN,,0,0,0,,I would just panic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.46,EN,,0,0,0,,and I was useless, I was absolutely useless
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.98,EN,,0,0,0,,But that said though, I really enjoyed it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.06,EN,,0,0,0,,It was a difficult part of the film to make
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.46,EN,,0,0,0,,It was very physically demanding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.86,EN,,0,0,0,,I dislocated my ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.50,EN,,0,0,0,,Right before the scene that we just watched
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.47,EN,,0,0,0,,where I'm running towards the car
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.74,EN,,0,0,0,,I was running, running and running
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.71,EN,,0,0,0,,and I just rolled over my ankle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.83,EN,,0,0,0,,and I sort of looked down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:13.08,EN,,0,0,0,,and my ankle was like looking the wrong way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.07,EN,,0,0,0,,And I was like oh god and then I stood on it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.44,EN,,0,0,0,,and it kind of went
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.00,EN,,0,0,0,,and it popped back in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.15,EN,,0,0,0,,So the last two weeks of shooting were brutal
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.65,EN,,0,0,0,,because my ankle was kind of broke were not broken
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.15,EN,,0,0,0,,but it wasn't the best
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:28.12,EN,,0,0,0,,But, yeah, it was an amazing experience to make a film like this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.38,EN,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's strange watching that again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.98,EN,,0,0,0,,Playing this character is one of the hardest things I've ever done
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.72,EN,,0,0,0,,physically and emotionally
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.70,EN,,0,0,0,,Ciarra Bravo and myself like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:54.69,EN,,0,0,0,,where we went emotionally to kind of bring these characters to life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.69,EN,,0,0,0,,was really difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.06,EN,,0,0,0,,So it's quite strange watching that again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.27,EN,,0,0,0,,That scene we shot on the last day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.70,EN,,0,0,0,,that was the last day of shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:06.33,EN,,0,0,0,,So a lot of that emotion there from that scene was very truthful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.33,0:05:09.03,EN,,0,0,0,,because it’s kind of me saying goodbye to the crew
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.05,EN,,0,0,0,,It's such an amazing story
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.60,EN,,0,0,0,,and it's maybe realize how brave the men and women are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.01,EN,,0,0,0,,who go overseas and fight for their country
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.62,EN,,0,0,0,,And it’s so sad that so many of them come home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.94,EN,,0,0,0,,and don't get the support that they deserve and that they need
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:26.29,EN,,0,0,0,,You know people sometimes can’t be medicated
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.63,EN,,0,0,0,,they need to be treated
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:31.28,EN,,0,0,0,,and therapy is something that has proven to help
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.33,EN,,0,0,0,,and drugs is something that proves to make people's life miserable
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.23,EN,,0,0,0,,So I really hope this film can be kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.68,EN,,0,0,0,,a spotlight on a problem that is right on our doorstep
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.23,EN,,0,0,0,,But it's an invisible problem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:49.57,EN,,0,0,0,,You know, substance abuse and especially, you know, opioid epidemic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.73,EN,,0,0,0,,It's a really sad one and one that I really hope that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.44,EN,,0,0,0,,we can kind of fight against
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:57.47,EN,,0,0,0,,I hope this film doesn't glamorize war or drugs in any shape or form
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:00.97,EN,,0,0,0,,I really think we were adamant to make this film be about not doing drugs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.57,EN,,0,0,0,,rather than romanticizing it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.81,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna keep watching
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.46,EN,,0,0,0,,To lighten the mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:14.03,EN,,0,0,0,,this, we called this rage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:17.98,EN,,0,0,0,,What was it? What did we call that thing on my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.61,EN,,0,0,0,,the toupee, the pel, that's what it was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.73,EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because I had a shaved head for the entire film
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.48,EN,,0,0,0,,Rachel, my make up artist had to be really strategic in the way
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:29.73,EN,,0,0,0,,that we would plan all the different looks throughout the course of the story
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:33.78,EN,,0,0,0,,and this look here is cherry coming home from Iraq
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:37.99,EN,,0,0,0,,and we really wanted to kind of do the short back and sides kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.88,EN,,0,0,0,,But I didn’t have time to grow my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.38,EN,,0,0,0,,so we had this like, pelt
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.50,EN,,0,0,0,,it was like a stick-on kind of toupee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.30,EN,,0,0,0,,and it looked ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.16,EN,,0,0,0,,but when it was on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.50,EN,,0,0,0,,it looked really cool
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.98,EN,,0,0,0,,but in the trailer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.89,EN,,0,0,0,,sometimes you’d see it looked like
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.70,EN,,0,0,0,,there was a dead squirrel in the trailer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:59.15,EN,,0,0,0,,So yeah, the toupee was great
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.10,EN,,0,0,0,,and I'm going to keep the toupee
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.81,EN,,0,0,0,,because my dad's not got the thickest head of hair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.26,EN,,0,0,0,,so I imagine one day I'm gonna lose my hair
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.82,EN,,0,0,0,,but it's okay because I have this glorious toupee
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.22,EN,,0,0,0,,that I can just throw up there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.45,EN,,0,0,0,,and I'll be all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.61,EN,,0,0,0,,*After the first class jimenez was killed in battle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.16,EN,,0,0,0,,*this soldier went on to take care of his platoon as well
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.35,EN,,0,0,0,,*Serving 3 platoons in total
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.82,EN,,0,0,0,,*to complete more combat missions
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.31,EN,,0,0,0,,get the fuck out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:33.84,EN,,0,0,0,,*any other medic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.23,EN,,0,0,0,,I just don't feel like I've done anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.77,EN,,0,1000,0,,to go running into a Chinese
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.85,EN,,1100,0,0,,It's totally me forgetting my line there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.48,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh my god
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.67,EN,,0,0,0,,That little pause where I go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.00,EN,,0,0,0,,I just don't feel like I've done anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.50,EN,,0,0,0,,to go running into a gymnasium about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.26,EN,,0,0,0,,in England we don't say gymnasium
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.26,0:07:47.61,EN,,0,0,0,,So that is me there
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.30,EN,,0,0,0,,like, in my head like, what's that fucking word again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.16,EN,,0,0,0,,oh, gymnasium came about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.56,EN,,0,0,0,,*This is my honor to present to you the medal of valor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.18,EN,,0,0,0,,my one true accomplishment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.48,EN,,0,0,0,,was not dying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.86,EN,,0,0,0,,I didn’t really have anything to do with that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.77,EN,,0,0,0,,*Congratulations! Specialist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.50,EN,,0,0,0,,*Thank you for yours service
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.55,EN,,0,0,0,,It’s interesting when you, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.78,EN,,0,0,0,,acting on camera
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.63,EN,,0,0,0,,You spend your entire time not looking at the camera
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.25,EN,,0,0,0,,Because it's called breaking the fourth wall
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.02,EN,,0,0,0,,and in this film we do it quite a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.84,EN,,0,0,0,,and it’s one of the hardest things I've ever done
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.51,EN,,0,0,0,,Because you spend so much time like drilling yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.80,EN,,0,0,0,,like do not look at the camera
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.85,EN,,0,0,0,,do not look at the camera
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.52,EN,,0,0,0,,then all of the sudden the camera is now part of the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.39,EN,,0,0,0,,and you have to address the camera and talk to it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.68,EN,,0,0,0,,and I suddenly became very self-conscious
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:32.11,EN,,0,0,0,,and aware that there are people watching you through the camera
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.56,EN,,0,0,0,,So all of the sudden it isn't just camera anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.83,EN,,0,0,0,,it's like a portal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.66,EN,,0,0,0,,and it used to really stress me out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.17,EN,,0,0,0,,but obviously I got over that stress
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:42.79,EN,,0,0,0,,and the film was fine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.36,EN,,0,0,0,,I like my hair tat you know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.81,EN,,0,0,0,,I might do that when I'm finished with Spiderman 3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.37,EN,,0,0,0,,Cut my hair like that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.36,EN,,0,0,0,,I think it suits me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.35,EN,,0,0,0,,Uh, it was an interesting feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.65,EN,,0,0,0,,putting on the army fatigues for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:36.82,EN,,0,0,0,,there was two feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.37,EN,,0,0,0,,One it felt really cool
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.88,EN,,0,0,0,,it was quite a cool costume
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.85,EN,,0,0,0,,but there was that other feeling where I didn’t deserve to wear it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.11,EN,,0,0,0,,I hadn't earned it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.77,EN,,0,0,0,,Something that you know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.25,EN,,0,0,0,,men and women really pushed themselves through a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.73,EN,,0,0,0,,to earn the right to wear those uniforms
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:54.76,EN,,0,0,0,,So I hope that through the hard work that I put into this film
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:59.81,EN,,0,0,0,,people who are soldiers now and are veterans will recognize that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.28,EN,,0,0,0,,and I hope I can do their stories justice
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.73,0:10:06.26,EN,,0,0,0,,but yeah it was an amazing day wearing it for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.31,EN,,0,0,0,,but a tricky one to figure out as well
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.21,EN,,0,0,0,,Emily drove me back to Ohio
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.20,EN,,0,0,0,,and I got to see her new house
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.33,EN,,0,0,0,,I started taking night classes at a school Emily was working at
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.41,EN,,0,0,0,,and I got a job that paid eight bucks an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.49,EN,,0,0,0,,I think one of the hardest thing about coming home for these soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.98,EN,,0,0,0,,is readjusting to normal life
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.62,EN,,0,0,0,,when they train and go through basic training
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.72,EN,,0,0,0,,they basically take civilians and then they turn them into killers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.61,EN,,0,0,0,,and they take the killers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.43,EN,,0,0,0,,and they just put them back into civilization
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.03,EN,,0,0,0,,and expect them to get on with their life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:10.81,EN,,0,0,0,,and I think that is where people find it really difficult to readjust
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.50,EN,,0,0,0,,and I hope that people watching this film
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.11,EN,,0,0,0,,will recognize how difficult that is for some people
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.87,EN,,0,0,0,,I love this film so much
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.31,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm so proud of it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.60,EN,,0,0,0,,We all work so hard to make this film what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.16,EN,,0,0,0,,So the fact was coming out soon
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.83,EN,,0,0,0,,and people have seen it and people have really enjoyed it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.65,EN,,0,0,0,,people are really impressed by it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.96,EN,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you like what that means to me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.53,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm really excited for Ciara
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.43,EN,,0,0,0,,I think people when they see her in this film
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:40.40,EN,,0,0,0,,are going to be absolutely blown away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:44.26,EN,,0,0,0,,and every single director in Hollywood is going to want to work with her
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:52.32,EN,,0,0,0,,I was so lucky that she was so ready to push herself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:56.08,EN,,0,0,0,,and to make this film as truthful as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.55,EN,,0,0,0,,Because the subject match of some of the stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.28,EN,,0,0,0,,that we were having to go through so dark
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.65,EN,,0,0,0,,and I'm so lucky that she was so ready to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.28,EN,,0,0,0,,This film could been a real nightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.78,EN,,0,0,0,,had myself and Emily not got alone
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.40,EN,,0,0,0,,and I'm so…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.90,EN,,0,0,0,,It was just great that we became really really good friends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.67,EN,,0,0,0,,and a really good team
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:13.71,EN,,0,0,0,,So I'm really excited to sit down and watch this with her
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.24,EN,,0,0,0,,and talk about how our lives have changed since making it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.97,EN,,0,0,0,,and the way we look at the world
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.21,EN,,0,0,0,,and the way we look at our industry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.99,EN,,0,0,0,,So, yeah I'm really really proud of this movie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.58,EN,,0,0,0,,and I'm really really excited for people to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.18,EN,,0,0,0,,and to hear what they think
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.20,EN,,0,0,0,,Guys this has been my GQ action replay of Cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.33,EN,,0,0,0,,Thank you for watching
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.61,EN,,0,0,0,,I hope you learned something new
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.31,EN,,0,0,0,,and I hope you enjoy the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.65,EN,,0,0,0,,Thank you again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.60,EN,,0,0,0,,Hey what's up guys I'm Tom Holland
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:41.16,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be doing a GQ action point replay
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Is that what it's called?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.70,EN,,0,0,0,,Hey what's up guys I'm Tom Holland
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.19,EN,,0,0,0,,We're going to be watching
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.24,EN,,0,0,0,,Now what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.89,EN,,0,0,0,,Why can't I remember this line
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.05,EN,,0,0,0,,That's what I get paid to do is remember lines
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.29,EN,,0,0,0,,and I can't remember it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.49,EN,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.14,EN,,0,0,0,,Take 327
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.51,EN,,0,0,0,,Hi I'm Tom Holland and we're going to be watching my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.34,EN,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.34,EN,,0,0,0,,My GQ action replay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.17,EN,,0,0,0,,{\an3}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.71,EN,,0,0,0,,That's what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.80,EN,,0,0,0,,Okay, here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.74,EN,,0,0,0,,Oh sorry I just banged your computer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.26,EN,,0,0,0,,I have this thing with John Watts
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.35,EN,,0,0,0,,who's the director of Spiderman
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.67,EN,,0,0,0,,I love him to bits
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:11.59,EN,,0,0,0,,I absolutely love him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.83,EN,,0,0,0,,I do anything for him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.79,EN,,0,0,0,,But the one thing he does that drives me mental
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.71,EN,,0,0,0,,is he always says one more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.74,EN,,0,0,0,,But he never does one more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.46,EN,,0,0,0,,They'll do like ten more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:22.99,EN,,0,0,0,,So now we have a jar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.36,EN,,0,0,0,,and every time he says one more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.21,EN,,0,0,0,,and he does more than one more
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.32,EN,,0,0,0,,He's got to put five bucks in the jar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.37,EN,,0,0,0,,And let me tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.50,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be rich
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.37,EN,,0,0,0,,Right let me do that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.75,EN,,0,0,0,,Sorry I keep banging your laptop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.37,EN,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.67,EN,,0,0,0,,Bang the table
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.87,EN,,0,0,0,,I reckon you can make a video
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.45,EN,,0,0,0,,just in their outtakes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.78,EN,,0,0,0,,The more entertaining than anything I have to say
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.28,EN,,0,0,0,,Hi there！It's Tom Hollaned here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:46.80,EN,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be watching my GQ action replay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.90,EN,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:48.78,EN,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:52.03,EN,,0,0,0,,And it's gonna be glorious
Comment: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,--------------------TEXT-CN--------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.78,CN,,0,0,0,,嗨，我是荷兰弟，这是GQ的观影回放
Dialogue: 1,0:00:03.78,0:00:06.47,CN,,0,0,0,,我们要看我最新出演的电影《谢里》
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.74,CN,,0,0,0,,罗素兄弟指导
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.00,0:00:28.61,CN,,0,0,0,,我们在伊拉克和摩洛哥拍摄
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.58,CN,,0,0,0,,一个叫Wazazet的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.58,0:00:32.48,CN,,0,0,0,,我忘了另一个地方叫什么了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.48,0:00:33.66,CN,,0,0,0,,但是我很喜欢那儿
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.66,0:00:35.01,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得那个地真的很惊艳
Dialogue: 1,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.25,CN,,0,0,0,,非常非常和善的原住民，特别友善
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.80,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得那里的食物也很不错
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.43,CN,,0,0,0,,我从未真正踏入过沙漠
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.97,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我对在沙漠中生活真的很感兴趣
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.97,0:00:46.54,CN,,0,0,0,,我们租了好些帐篷，在沙漠中露营
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.54,0:00:47.61,CN,,0,0,0,,还骑了骆驼
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.61,0:00:48.28,CN,,0,0,0,,真的很酷
Dialogue: 1,0:00:48.28,0:00:50.02,CN,,0,0,0,,那是一段我很享受的，非常美好的时光
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.50,CN,,0,0,0,,噢天，这么说太英国口音了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.57,CN,,0,0,0,,我得改改
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.57,0:01:14.80,CN,,0,0,0,,我就说，“一点儿”，而不是“一点”
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.85,0:01:18.92,CN,,0,0,0,,我得把这个记下来
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.92,0:01:22.03,CN,,0,0,0,,还得跟他们说我们要在放映之前重新录一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.03,0:01:23.91,CN,,0,0,0,,等下，”一点儿“
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.19,CN,,0,0,0,,真不错，还有点儿工作要做
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.20,0:01:29.08,CN,,0,0,0,,你确定你没事吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.20,CN,,0,0,0,,我只是想你了，没了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.52,CN,,0,0,0,,我也想你
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.51,0:01:36.81,CN,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.53,0:01:38.67,CN,,0,0,0,,草
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.61,0:01:42.88,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一处很有意思的哭戏
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.88,0:01:46.60,CN,,0,0,0,,哭有时候真的很简单
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.92,CN,,0,0,0,,但是有时候又很难
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.92,0:01:51.55,CN,,0,0,0,,之前我们录蜘蛛侠3的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.92,CN,,0,0,0,,我可以直接打开这种模式
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.68,CN,,0,0,0,,但是我没有，我当时就觉得这太妙了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.68,0:01:56.96,CN,,0,0,0,,如果我可以每次都这样
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.96,0:02:01.10,CN,,0,0,0,,这一定很棒，但有时候你想哭却哭不出来
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.10,0:02:03.51,CN,,0,0,0,,但是，反正有很多方法让你哭出来
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.51,0:02:04.98,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候我通过听音乐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.94,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候我和亲近的人交心地谈话
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.57,CN,,0,0,0,,可以是我哥哥，或者雷切尔，安东尼，或者是任何一个我的同事
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.94,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候我得仔细想想
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.94,0:02:16.92,CN,,0,0,0,,那些过去发生的让我真的很伤心的事
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.92,0:02:18.17,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候我得想想
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.67,CN,,0,0,0,,那些可能会发生让我感觉很难过的事
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.67,0:02:22.64,CN,,0,0,0,,有很多不同的方式让你哭泣
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.64,0:02:24.76,CN,,0,0,0,,你只需要有耐心
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.85,CN,,0,0,0,,也不要因为有人在等你而感到压迫
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.85,0:02:29.50,CN,,0,0,0,,她的部分是在克利夫兰拍的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.88,CN,,0,0,0,,明显，我这部分是在摩洛哥拍的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.88,0:02:36.57,CN,,0,0,0,,诚实地说，我把我的台词当作一个..
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.57,0:02:39.74,CN,,0,0,0,,也就有6英尺2英寸高
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.74,0:02:41.23,CN,,0,0,0,,他的则是个大块头写的
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.23,0:02:45.05,CN,,0,0,0,,所以，这个事有点棘手
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.05,0:02:47.04,CN,,0,0,0,,因为希亚拉没有和我一起拍
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.98,CN,,0,0,0,,我都要在电话里哭了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.61,CN,,0,0,0,,克里斯卡斯蒂就说
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.61,0:02:53.09,CN,,0,0,0,,”宝贝，你是看到什么不好的事情了吗？“
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.09,0:02:54.66,CN,,0,0,0,,我看着他
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.97,CN,,0,0,0,,”我一个大男人，叫我宝贝干什么？“
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.99,CN,,0,0,0,,然后一切好像变得轻松一些了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.99,0:03:03.99,CN,,0,0,0,,现在我每次看电影都得哭
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.65,CN,,0,0,0,,这确实挺丢人的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.65,0:03:06.76,CN,,0,0,0,,我不知道我究竟怎么了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.66,CN,,0,0,0,,就好像经历了一个我从不会为任何事哭泣的阶段
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.06,CN,,0,0,0,,到我现在基本上每次都得哭
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.52,0:03:16.41,CN,,0,0,0,,我不会一周哭很多次，但是我确实老哭
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.59,CN,,0,0,0,,现在就要哭了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.73,CN,,0,0,0,,现在我哭的不那么多了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.73,0:03:23.10,CN,,0,0,0,,不过，我还是总是哭
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.50,CN,,0,0,0,,哎，管他呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.62,CN,,0,0,0,,我们做了很多作战训练
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.44,CN,,0,0,0,,我发现我可能会是世界上最差的士兵
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.44,0:03:41.40,CN,,0,0,0,,很明显，我在剧中扮演一位医疗兵
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.45,CN,,0,0,0,,我做了很多训练，然后变成了军医
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.73,CN,,0,0,0,,每次他们说开机
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.18,CN,,0,0,0,,子弹出膛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.74,CN,,0,0,0,,然后爆炸也开始了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.74,0:03:51.17,CN,,0,0,0,,我就只会害怕
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.46,CN,,0,0,0,,我很没用，完全没用
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.98,CN,,0,0,0,,尽管这么说吧，我还是很享受
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.06,CN,,0,0,0,,这是电影中很难拍的部分
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.06,0:03:59.46,CN,,0,0,0,,很消耗体力
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.86,CN,,0,0,0,,我脚腕错位了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.50,CN,,0,0,0,,就在我们刚刚看到的那一幕前
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.47,CN,,0,0,0,,我当时正好往车那边跑
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.44,0:04:06.74,CN,,0,0,0,,我就跑啊，跑啊，跑
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.71,CN,,0,0,0,,我翻了个跟头扭到脚踝
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.83,CN,,0,0,0,,我往下看了看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.83,0:04:13.08,CN,,0,0,0,,我的脚腕看起来是往错误的方向撇了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.07,CN,,0,0,0,,然后我当时，噢天，我就站上去了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.44,CN,,0,0,0,,脚踝就有点往旁边拐
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.00,CN,,0,0,0,,它突然又回来了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.15,CN,,0,0,0,,所以最后两周的拍摄很残忍
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.65,CN,,0,0,0,,因为我对脚踝有点问题，但是没骨折
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.15,CN,,0,0,0,,但是不是最佳状态
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.15,0:04:28.12,CN,,0,0,0,,但是，能参与这样的电影的拍摄确实是一种很棒的体验
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.38,CN,,0,0,0,,哇，再看一遍真的有点奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.38,0:04:46.98,CN,,0,0,0,,表演这个角色是我做过最难的事情之一
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.72,CN,,0,0,0,,体力上，情感上都是
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.70,CN,,0,0,0,,希亚拉博拉沃和我都是
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.70,0:04:54.69,CN,,0,0,0,,当我们试图在情感上把这俩个角色带入生活时
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.69,0:04:56.69,CN,,0,0,0,,真的很难
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.14,0:04:59.06,CN,,0,0,0,,所以再看一遍真的有点奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.27,CN,,0,0,0,,我们最后一天拍摄的那个场景
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.70,CN,,0,0,0,,那是最后一天拍摄
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.70,0:05:06.33,CN,,0,0,0,,所以在那个场景里面，很多感情都是真实的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.33,0:05:09.03,CN,,0,0,0,,因为对于我来说也是和工作人员说再见
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.03,0:05:11.05,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一个多么令人感叹的故事
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.05,0:05:14.60,CN,,0,0,0,,它也让我意识到男人和女人是多么的勇敢
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.60,0:05:17.01,CN,,0,0,0,,那些远渡重洋为国家战斗的人们
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.62,CN,,0,0,0,,而且很难过的是听到很多人回家以后
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.94,CN,,0,0,0,,没有得到他们应得的、需要的支持
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.94,0:05:26.29,CN,,0,0,0,,你知道人有时候是用药无法治愈的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.63,CN,,0,0,0,,他们需要治疗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.81,0:05:31.28,CN,,0,0,0,,疗法是被证实有用的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.28,0:05:35.33,CN,,0,0,0,,而毒品则是被证实让生活变得可悲的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.63,0:05:39.23,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我真心希望这部电影
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.68,CN,,0,0,0,,可以聚焦在我们家门口的问题
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.23,CN,,0,0,0,,但是这是隐形的问题
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.23,0:05:49.57,CN,,0,0,0,,你知道，药物滥用，尤其是阿片类药物流行
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.73,CN,,0,0,0,,这是一件很难过的事情，一件我真心希望
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.44,CN,,0,0,0,,我们可以抗争的事情
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.44,0:05:57.47,CN,,0,0,0,,我希望这部电影不要以任何形式美化战争或毒品
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.47,0:06:00.97,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的认为我们坚持要让这部电影的目的是远离毒品
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.57,CN,,0,0,0,,而不是美化毒品
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.81,CN,,0,0,0,,我们继续看
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.46,CN,,0,0,0,,为了点亮情绪
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.46,0:06:14.03,CN,,0,0,0,,我们叫它 盛怒
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.03,0:06:17.98,CN,,0,0,0,,是什么?我头上的东西叫什么来着?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.61,CN,,0,0,0,,假发，就是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.73,CN,,0,0,0,,因为我在开拍之前把头发剃光了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.48,CN,,0,0,0,,雷切尔，我的化妆师在这方面很有策略
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.48,0:06:29.73,CN,,0,0,0,,我们会在整个故事中设计出各种不同的造型
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.73,0:06:33.78,CN,,0,0,0,,这里的这个造型是谢里从伊拉克回家的造型
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.78,0:06:37.99,CN,,0,0,0,,我们真的很想把后脑勺和两侧剪短
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.88,CN,,0,0,0,,但是我没时间长头发了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.38,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我们找了这个，假发片
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.38,0:06:45.50,CN,,0,0,0,,就像一种贴上去的假发
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.30,CN,,0,0,0,,它看上去不可思议
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.16,CN,,0,0,0,,但是当戴上它时
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.50,CN,,0,0,0,,看起来真的很酷
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.98,CN,,0,0,0,,但是在预告片中
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.89,CN,,0,0,0,,有时候你会看到它看起来
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.70,CN,,0,0,0,,像拖车里有只死松鼠
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.70,0:06:59.15,CN,,0,0,0,,所以，假发片真的很不错
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.10,CN,,0,0,0,,我会把假发片保留起来
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.81,CN,,0,0,0,,因为我爸头发就不是很多
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.26,CN,,0,0,0,,我想着有一天我脱发了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.82,CN,,0,0,0,,没关系，我有这个漂亮的假发片
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.22,CN,,0,0,0,,我可以直接粘上去
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.45,CN,,0,0,0,,然后我就有头发了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.88,0:07:24.61,CN,,0,0,0,,*当一等兵希门尼斯在战斗中阵亡后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.15,0:07:28.16,CN,,0,0,0,,*这个士兵继续照顾他的排
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.35,CN,,0,0,0,,*总共为3个排提供服务
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.82,CN,,0,0,0,,*以完成更多战斗任务
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.31,CN,,0,0,0,,他妈的离开这里
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.31,0:07:33.84,CN,,0,0,0,,*任何其他医疗兵
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.84,0:07:35.23,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的没感觉我做了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.77,CN,,0,1000,0,,碰到一个中国人
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.33,0:07:38.85,CN,,1100,0,0,,这里我完全忘了我的台词了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.85,0:07:39.48,CN,,0,0,0,,噢天
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.67,CN,,0,0,0,,这里我的一点小停顿
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.00,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的没感觉我做了什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.50,CN,,0,0,0,,去健身房跑步
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.26,CN,,0,0,0,,在英格兰我们不说健身房
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.26,0:07:47.61,CN,,0,0,0,,所以这里就是我了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.30,CN,,0,0,0,,就，我脑子里就在想，这个破词到底是什么
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.30,0:07:52.16,CN,,0,0,0,,噢，健身房这个词出现了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.56,CN,,0,0,0,,*我很荣幸向你颁发英勇勋章
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.56,0:07:57.18,CN,,0,0,0,,我一项真正的成就
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.18,0:07:58.48,CN,,0,0,0,,就是没有死去
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.86,CN,,0,0,0,,这跟我一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.77,CN,,0,0,0,,*祝贺你！专家！
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.77,0:08:03.50,CN,,0,0,0,,*感谢你的服役
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.55,CN,,0,0,0,,当你..真的很有趣
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.78,CN,,0,0,0,,面对相机表演
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.63,CN,,0,0,0,,你把所有时间都花在不看镜头上
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.25,CN,,0,0,0,,因为这叫做打破第四堵墙
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.02,CN,,0,0,0,,在电影中我们经常那么做
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.84,CN,,0,0,0,,这是我做过最艰难的事
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.51,CN,,0,0,0,,因为你花了那么多时间使自己沉浸
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.80,CN,,0,0,0,,因为不需要看镜头
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.85,CN,,0,0,0,,不要看镜头
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.52,CN,,0,0,0,,然后突然间镜头就成了场景的一部分
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.52,0:08:25.39,CN,,0,0,0,,你必须对着镜头说话
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.68,CN,,0,0,0,,我自我意识忽然就很强
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.68,0:08:32.11,CN,,0,0,0,,意识到人们正在通过镜头看你
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.56,CN,,0,0,0,,忽然它就不只是相机了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.83,CN,,0,0,0,,它就像一个传送门
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.83,0:08:38.66,CN,,0,0,0,,这曾经让我压力山大
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.66,0:08:41.17,CN,,0,0,0,,但显然我承受住了压力
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.17,0:08:42.79,CN,,0,0,0,,这部电影还好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.36,CN,,0,0,0,,我喜欢我的头发
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.81,CN,,0,0,0,,我好像是在拍完蜘蛛侠3时候做的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.37,CN,,0,0,0,,把我的头发剪成这样
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.37,0:09:11.36,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得它很适合我
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.35,CN,,0,0,0,,那确实是很有趣的感觉
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.65,CN,,0,0,0,,第一次穿上军装
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.65,0:09:36.82,CN,,0,0,0,,当时我有两种感受
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.37,CN,,0,0,0,,第一是，它感觉真酷
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.37,0:09:39.88,CN,,0,0,0,,真是一件很酷的制服
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.85,CN,,0,0,0,,但另一种感受是我不觉得我配得上穿它
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.85,0:09:44.11,CN,,0,0,0,,我没有为它争取过
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.77,CN,,0,0,0,,一些，你知道
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.77,0:09:48.25,CN,,0,0,0,,男人和女人们真的很努力
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.73,CN,,0,0,0,,为了自己能穿上这些军装
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.73,0:09:54.76,CN,,0,0,0,,所以我希望通过我在这部电影里投入的努力
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.77,0:09:59.81,CN,,0,0,0,,现役军人和退伍军人的人会认识到这一点
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.81,0:10:02.28,CN,,0,0,0,,我希望我能公正地讲述他们的故事
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.73,0:10:06.26,CN,,0,0,0,,但是确实，穿上它真的是很棒的一天
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.31,CN,,0,0,0,,但是也意识到这有些棘手
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.17,0:10:13.21,CN,,0,0,0,,艾米莉开车送我回俄亥俄
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.20,CN,,0,0,0,,我得以看见她新房子
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.33,CN,,0,0,0,,我开始在艾米莉工作的学校上夜校
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.41,CN,,0,0,0,,我找到了一份时薪八美元的工作
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.49,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得其中最难的一件事是当士兵们回到家乡
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.49,0:10:55.98,CN,,0,0,0,,重新适应正常的的生活
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.62,CN,,0,0,0,,当他们进行基本训练时
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.72,CN,,0,0,0,,他们绑架平民然后把他们变成杀手
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.61,CN,,0,0,0,,现在他们把杀手
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.43,CN,,0,0,0,,试图变回普通平民
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.03,CN,,0,0,0,,希望他们能够继续他们的生活
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.03,0:11:10.81,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得这就是人们觉得很难适应的一点
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.50,CN,,0,0,0,,我希望看到这部影片的人们
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.11,CN,,0,0,0,,可以意识到对于这些人来说有多么难
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.87,CN,,0,0,0,,我太喜欢这部片子了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.31,CN,,0,0,0,,我很自豪
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.82,0:11:24.60,CN,,0,0,0,,我们都很努力才让这部电影成为今天的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.16,0:11:28.16,CN,,0,0,0,,所以事实上这部电影很快就要上映了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.83,CN,,0,0,0,,人们看到了它，也很喜欢它
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.65,CN,,0,0,0,,人们都觉得很惊艳
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.96,CN,,0,0,0,,我很难告诉你它对于我真正意味着什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.53,CN,,0,0,0,,我也很为希亚拉激动
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.43,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得人们看到电影里的她时
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.43,0:11:40.40,CN,,0,0,0,,会被完全震撼
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.40,0:11:44.26,CN,,0,0,0,,好莱坞里每一个导演都会想和她合作
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.26,0:11:52.32,CN,,0,0,0,,我很幸运，她准备强迫自己做到最好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.86,0:11:56.08,CN,,0,0,0,,让这部片越真实越好
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.55,CN,,0,0,0,,因为有些东西的主题是吻合的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.28,CN,,0,0,0,,我们得各自在暗中进行
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.65,CN,,0,0,0,,我很开心，她准备好这么做了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.28,CN,,0,0,0,,这部电影可能是一场真正的噩梦
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.78,CN,,0,0,0,,我和艾米丽分别拍摄
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.40,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的很…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.40,0:12:09.90,CN,,0,0,0,,我们能够成为很好的朋友真是不错
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.67,CN,,0,0,0,,也是很好的团队
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.67,0:12:13.71,CN,,0,0,0,,所以能够坐下来看她表演我真的很激动
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.71,0:12:16.24,CN,,0,0,0,,谈谈我们的生活自从拍摄它以来发生了怎样的变化
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.97,CN,,0,0,0,,我们看待世界的方式
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.97,0:12:20.21,CN,,0,0,0,,我们看待产业的方式
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.99,CN,,0,0,0,,所以，我真的对这个电影十分自豪
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.99,0:12:25.58,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的真的很期待人们看到它
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.18,CN,,0,0,0,,听听他们的想法
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.18,0:12:30.20,CN,,0,0,0,,大家好，这是GQ对《谢里》的观影回放
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.33,CN,,0,0,0,,感谢观看
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.61,CN,,0,0,0,,我希望你学到些新的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.61,0:12:34.31,CN,,0,0,0,,我希望你享受这部电影
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.65,CN,,0,0,0,,再次感谢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.60,CN,,0,0,0,,嗨！最近怎么样？我是荷兰弟
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.60,0:12:41.16,CN,,0,0,0,,我将要做一个GQ的观影回放
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.14,CN,,0,0,0,,是这么叫的吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.70,CN,,0,0,0,,嗨！最近怎么样？我是荷兰弟
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.19,CN,,0,0,0,,我们将要看
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.24,CN,,0,0,0,,现在该说什么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.21,0:12:48.89,CN,,0,0,0,,为什么我记不住台词啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.05,CN,,0,0,0,,我的工作就是记住台词
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.29,CN,,0,0,0,,但是我记不住
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.29,0:12:53.49,CN,,0,0,0,,行吧，我们开始
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.49,0:12:55.14,CN,,0,0,0,,第327次拍摄
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.51,CN,,0,0,0,,嗨我是荷兰弟，我们将要看我的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.34,CN,,0,0,0,,什么来着？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.34,CN,,0,0,0,,我的GQ的观影回放
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.34,0:13:02.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\an3}对了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.71,CN,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.80,CN,,0,0,0,,行，我们再来
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.74,CN,,0,0,0,,噢对不起，我刚刚拍你电脑来着
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.26,CN,,0,0,0,,我和约翰·瓦茨经常这样
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.26,0:13:09.35,CN,,0,0,0,,他是蜘蛛侠的导演
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.67,CN,,0,0,0,,我喜欢他拍
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.67,0:13:11.59,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的很爱他
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.59,0:13:12.83,CN,,0,0,0,,我愿意为他做任何事
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.83,0:13:15.79,CN,,0,0,0,,但他做的有件事让我抓狂
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.71,CN,,0,0,0,,就是他总是说再来一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.74,CN,,0,0,0,,但是他不止再来一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.46,CN,,0,0,0,,他可能会再来十遍
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.46,0:13:22.99,CN,,0,0,0,,我们现在得要一个罐子
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.36,CN,,0,0,0,,每次他说，再来一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.36,0:13:26.21,CN,,0,0,0,,他这么做了不止一次
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.21,0:13:28.32,CN,,0,0,0,,那么他就要在罐子里放5美元
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.37,CN,,0,0,0,,我跟你讲
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.50,CN,,0,0,0,,我会变得富有的
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.50,0:13:31.37,CN,,0,0,0,,就让我这么做
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.75,CN,,0,0,0,,不好意思，我一直在拍你的电脑
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.37,CN,,0,0,0,,我真的太抱歉了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.67,CN,,0,0,0,,拍桌子吧那就
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.87,CN,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可以做个视频
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.87,0:13:38.45,CN,,0,0,0,,就用他们拍的这些片段
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.45,0:13:40.78,CN,,0,0,0,,比我要说的任何事都有趣
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.28,CN,,0,0,0,,嗨！这里是荷兰弟
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.28,0:13:46.80,CN,,0,0,0,,我们将要看我的GQ观影回放
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.28,0:13:47.90,CN,,0,0,0,,现在对了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.90,0:13:48.78,CN,,0,0,0,,嗯哼
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.78,0:13:52.03,CN,,0,0,0,,这一定会很精彩的
